input_lb: Do' maré ubur kuan Tuhan, ngaceku Ieh neninger tawarku mutuh pedengan.
raw_output: When I cry out to the Lord, I know He hears my prayer for help.
processed_output: When I cry out to the Lord, I know He hears my prayer for help.
reference: Blessed be Yahweh, because he has heard the voice of my petitions.

Yahweh’s word came to me again, saying,

input_lb: Idi kebala Musa nedeh, "Kudeng ini bala Tuhan Allah lun Israil, Do' anid- anid muyuh ngabin pelapet idi nalan lemaba su luk inan lupo, rat tanga' selipa macing ku tanga' luk paped selipa, idi do' muyuh ngaté kinanak muyuh, rurum muyuh, idi lun dengan muyuh.”
raw_output: Then Moses said, “This is what the LORD, the God of Israel, says: Let each of you put his sword on his side, go in and out from gate to gate throughout the camp, and let each of you kill his brother, his companion, and his neighbor.”
processed_output: Then Moses said, “This is what the LORD, the God of Israel, says: Let each of you put his sword on his side, go in and out from gate to gate throughout the camp, and let each of you kill his brother, his companion, and his neighbor.”
reference: He said to them, “Yahweh, the God of Israel, says, ‘Every man put his sword on his thigh, and go back and forth from gate to gate throughout the camp, and every man kill his brother, and every man his companion, and every man his neighbor.’”
